<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>leg-show • show a leg</xh5><p> <i>leg-show</i>—a theatrical performance by scantily-dressed women: At a <u>leg-show</u> of these days you saw far less of the female form than is now exhibited in the streets.</p><p> <i>show a leg—</i>is used to urge people to get up or do smth. with more effort: In the morning, the boatswain’s mate would awaken the crew with the cry “<u>show a leg</u>.”</p> </entry>
